## 7. Product Listing

### Goal

Present available HVAC equipment options with real-time pricing and availability so the homeowner can compare and select their preferred system.

### Journey

**Entry:**
- Customizations â†’ Product Listing
- Back action from Product Details

**Steps:** (non-linear â€” homeowner and sales rep browse options)
- View list of available equipment options
- Compare pricing, efficiency ratings, and features
- Filter or sort options
- Select equipment to view details or proceed to checkout

**Exit:**
- Select product â†’ Product Details
- Edit customizations â†’ Customizations
- Back â†’ Energy Usage or Customizations
- Quick select (if enabled) â†’ Summary & Checkout

### Functionality

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Display equipment options | Show available systems with brand, model, efficiency rating, price, and estimated savings |
| Real-time availability | Only show equipment confirmed available from Sibi inventory |
| Pricing display | Show total price after rebates and commission adjustments |
| Comparison features | [FUTURE] Side-by-side comparison of 2-3 options |
| Sort options | Sort by price, efficiency, brand, or recommended |
| Filter options | Filter by brand, efficiency tier, price range |
| Equipment size adjustment | [TBD] Quick toggle to change tonnage without returning to Customizations |
| Add condenser quick action | [TBD] Option to add condenser from this screen |

### Components

*Reference: engineering/design-system.md*

| Functionality | Recommended Components |
|---------------|------------------------|
| Equipment options display | Card list or grid layout (reference existing onboarding product listing) |
| Sort/filter controls | Dropdown or segmented controls |
| Price display | Prominent text with original/discounted price if applicable |
| Quick actions | Button (secondary) for edit customizations |
| Recommended badge | StatusTag (info variant) for recommended option |

### Edge Cases

| Scenario | Expected Behavior |
|----------|-------------------|
| No products available | Display message explaining unavailability, suggest adjusting customizations or contacting support |
| Limited options (1-2 products) | Display available options without empty state messaging |
| Price changes during session | Refresh prices on return to this screen, notify if significant change |
| Product becomes unavailable | Remove from list, if previously selected show message |

### Error States

| Error Condition | User Message | Recovery Action |
|-----------------|--------------|-----------------|
| Inventory API unavailable | We're having trouble loading equipment options. Please try again. | Retry action, contact support link |
| Pricing API unavailable | Pricing information is temporarily unavailable. Prices shown may not be current. | Show cached prices with disclaimer |

