## 8. Product Details

### Goal

Provide comprehensive information about a selected HVAC system including equipment configuration, specifications, installation inclusions, and financing options to support the homeowner's purchase decision and facilitate same-visit closing.

### Journey

**Entry:**
- Product Listing â†’ Product Details (on product selection)
- "Other compatible systems" carousel â†’ Product Details (alternative selection)

**Steps:**
1. System displays configuration summary bar with selected equipment components
2. Sales rep presents hero section with key value proposition and benefits
3. Sales rep reviews "What's Included" service and equipment lists with homeowner
4. Homeowner can explore detailed tech specs for each equipment type
5. Sales rep addresses common questions using expandable FAQ section
6. Homeowner optionally views alternative compatible systems
7. Homeowner decides to proceed via sticky footer or return to listing

**Exit:**
- "Choose System" CTA â†’ Summary & Checkout
- "Price Breakdown" link â†’ Pricing detail modal or inline expansion
- "View" configuration â†’ Configuration detail modal
- Select alternative system â†’ Product Details (for selected system)
- Back navigation â†’ Product Listing

### Page Sections

The Product Details page consists of the following sections in order:

| Section | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| Configuration Bar | Summary of selected equipment components with edit access |
| Hero Section | Primary product presentation with brand, title, benefits, and key selling points |
| Safety/Requirements Alert | Warnings about additional requirements (e.g., water heater upgrade) |
| What's Included | Complete breakdown of service inclusions and equipment list |
| Tech Specs | Detailed technical specifications for all equipment types |
| FAQ | Expandable frequently asked questions |
| Other Compatible Systems | Horizontal carousel of alternative product options |
| Sticky Footer | Persistent pricing summary and primary CTA |

### Functionality

#### Configuration Bar

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Display selected configuration | Show summary of equipment components (e.g., "5x Wall units Â· 1x Ceiling unit Â· 2x Condensers") |
| Configuration label | "Your configuration" header text |
| View action | Button to expand full configuration details in modal or inline |
| Scroll persistence | Bar remains visible or accessible as user scrolls |

#### Hero Section

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Brand logo display | Show manufacturer logo (e.g., Mitsubishi) prominently |
| Product title | Clear, benefit-oriented headline (e.g., "An affordable heating and cooling solution") |
| Product description | Brief paragraph explaining the system and its benefits |
| Hero image | Large product photography showing the primary equipment |
| Key selling points | Checkmark-prefixed benefit statements highlighting: |
| | - Installation speed ("Can be installed within days") |
| | - Price positioning ("This is the most affordable system") |
| | - Rebate savings ("Save $X,XXX â€” hassle free!") |
| Feature icons | Visual indicators for system capabilities (Heat & AC, Ductless, Electricity powered) |

#### Safety/Requirements Alert

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Display requirement warning | Yellow alert banner for additional requirements |
| Warning content | Explain requirement clearly (e.g., "For your safety, installing this system requires a new water heater as well.") |
| Learn more link | Link to additional information about the requirement |
| Conditional display | Only show when applicable to selected system |

#### What's Included Section

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Section header | "What's included?" with subheadline "Tetra offers an end-to-end installation" |
| Service column | List of included services with icons: |
| | - Installation |
| | - All equipment needed |
| | - All materials |
| | - Rebate & loan paperwork |
| | - 0% Interest financing |
| | - Equipment removal |
| | - Electrical work |
| Equipment column | List of included equipment with quantities: |
| | - [X]x Heat Pump Condensers |
| | - [X]x Wall Units |
| | - [X]x Ceiling Cassette |
| | - [X]x Branch Box |
| | - Foundation/Coring |
| | - Electrical work |
| | - Equipment removal |
| Trust indicators | Google rating display (e.g., "4.7 stars on Google") with review count |
| Service image | Photo of installation team or work in progress |
| Info icons | Tooltip icons on select items for additional explanation |

