#### Other Compatible Systems Section

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Section header | "Other compatible systems" with subheadline "Tetra offers hundreds of systems. Not sure about this one? Check out your options." |
| System count indicator | Display number of alternatives (e.g., "5 Systems") |
| Horizontal carousel | Scrollable row of alternative system cards |
| Navigation arrows | Left/right arrows for carousel navigation |
| Alternative system cards | For each alternative, display: |
| | - System type label (e.g., "Heat pump") |
| | - System name (e.g., "LG Ductless Heat Pump") |
| | - Brand logo |
