| | - Monthly price |
| | - Payback period |
| | - 1st year savings |
| | - Lifetime savings |
| | - "Select" action button |

#### Sticky Footer

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Product identifier | System name and brand (e.g., "Carrier Ductless Heat Pump") |
| Monthly price | Prominent monthly payment amount with period (e.g., "$148/mo") |
| Payment terms | Loan terms in smaller text (e.g., "for 120 month loan") |
| Total price | Full price after rebates (e.g., "$12,480" with "after IRA rebate if applicable" note) |
| Price breakdown link | "Price Breakdown" link to detailed cost breakdown |
| Primary CTA | "Choose System" button to proceed to checkout |
| Incentive program icons | Visual indicators for applicable rebate programs |
| Footer persistence | Sticky positioning at bottom of viewport |

### Components

*Reference: engineering/design-system.md*

| Section | Recommended Components |
|---------|------------------------|
| Configuration Bar | Custom bar with Button (secondary) for "View" action |
| Hero Section | Image display, brand logo, heading styles, Checkmark icons for benefits |
| Safety Alert | SystemAlertBanner (warning variant) |
| What's Included | Two-column layout, icon list, InfoRow or checklist items |
| Tech Specs | Tab navigation or column layout, specification table, image thumbnails |
| FAQ | Accordion/CollapsibleSectionHeader components |
| Other Systems Carousel | Horizontal scroll container, product cards with Button (secondary) |
| Sticky Footer | StickyFooter with custom content, Button (primary) for CTA |

### Edge Cases

| Scenario | Expected Behavior |
|----------|-------------------|
| System with no alternatives | Hide "Other Compatible Systems" section entirely |
| Configuration requires additional equipment | Show Safety/Requirements Alert with clear explanation |
| Multiple equipment variants available | Show separate spec columns for each variant |
| Long FAQ answers | Ensure expandable area handles variable content length |
| Product image unavailable | Display placeholder image with brand logo |
| Rebate eligibility uncertain | Show price with "if applicable" qualifier |
| Mobile viewport | Stack columns vertically, adjust carousel to single-card view |
| Tech specs missing for equipment type | Show available specs with "N/A" for missing values |

### Error States

| Error Condition | User Message | Recovery Action |
|-----------------|--------------|-----------------|
| Product data load failed | We couldn't load this product's details. Please try again. | Retry action, return to listing |
| Pricing calculation failed | Pricing information is temporarily unavailable. Please try again. | Retry action, show cached price if available |
| Alternative systems unavailable | We couldn't load alternative options. | Hide carousel section, allow continuation |
| Configuration details unavailable | Configuration details unavailable. | Show basic summary, allow continuation |

### Design Notes

**Visual Hierarchy:**
- Configuration bar establishes context immediately
- Hero section drives emotional engagement with benefit-focused messaging
- Tech specs serve as reference material for detail-oriented buyers
- Sticky footer ensures CTA is always accessible

**Content Strategy:**
- Lead with benefits (hero), follow with proof (what's included, trust indicators)
- Technical details available but not primary focus
- FAQ addresses objections proactively
- Alternative options reduce fear of wrong choice

**Mobile Considerations:**
- Sticky footer critical for mobile conversion
- Tech specs should be horizontally scrollable or use tabs
- Alternative systems carousel should show one card at a time
- FAQ accordion essential for managing content length

---

## 9. Summary & Checkout

### Goal

Present a comprehensive review of all selections and enable homeowners to finalize payment method, scheduling, and quote sharing before proceeding to deposit collection.

### Journey

**Entry:**
- Product Details â†’ Summary & Checkout
- Direct link from saved quote (returning user)

**Steps:**
1. System displays complete quote summary (equipment, rebates, total)
2. Homeowner reviews all selections for accuracy
3. Homeowner selects payment method (cash, loan, lease)
4. If financing selected, system initiates credit check with Palmetto
5. System displays available installation windows
6. Homeowner selects preferred installation time
7. Sales rep optionally sends quote via email or text for homeowner review
8. Homeowner confirms to proceed to deposit

**Exit:**
- Confirm and proceed â†’ Deposit
- Financing denied â†’ Display alternatives (cash, different financing option)
- Send quote (without deposit) â†’ Session ends, quote saved for later
- Back â†’ Product Details
- Edit selections â†’ Product Details or Customizations

### Functionality

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Display equipment summary | Show selected equipment with image, name, specifications summary |
| Display pricing breakdown | Equipment cost, installation, rebates applied, taxes (if applicable), final total |
| Dual pricing format | Show both monthly payment amount and total price throughout |
| Payment method selection | Options: Cash, Loan, Lease with monthly payment preview for financing options |
| Credit check initiation | For loan/lease, submit application to Palmetto financing [CLARIFICATION NEEDED: credit check flow details] |
| Installation scheduling | Display available installation windows from Sibi, allow selection of preferred date/time |
| Edit capability | Allow returning to previous screens to modify selections |
| Send quote via email | Generate formatted quote summary and send to homeowner's email address |
| Send quote via text | Send SMS with link to quote summary for homeowner |
| Proceed to deposit | Confirm selections and advance to payment collection |
| Incentive programs display | Show supported rebate/incentive program logos (NYSERDA, PSEG, etc.) |

### Components

*Reference: engineering/design-system.md*

| Functionality | Recommended Components |
|---------------|------------------------|
| Equipment summary | VisitSummaryCard or product card with image |
| Pricing breakdown | PaymentBreakdown with dual pricing display |
| Payment method options | Selectable cards with radio selection |
| Financing preview | Inline calculation showing monthly payment for each option |
| Installation windows | TimeSlotCard options |
| Contact info fields | Input (email), Input (phone) |
| Send quote actions | Button (secondary) |
| Edit links | Text links or Button (secondary) |
| Proceed action | Button (primary), StickyFooter |
| Incentive logos | Image row in footer area |

### Changes from v1.1

| Previous Behavior | New Behavior | Rationale |
|-------------------|--------------|-----------|
| Deposit collection on this screen | Move deposit collection to dedicated Deposit screen | Proven conversion pattern from existing ecommerce; reduces cognitive load at decision point |
| Single price display | Add dual pricing (monthly + total) throughout | Matches existing ecommerce pattern; helps homeowners understand financing impact |
| Generic checkout flow | Add "Edit" capability to return to previous screens | Allows corrections without starting over |
| No incentive program visibility | Add supported incentive programs display | Builds trust and reminds homeowners of savings |

### Edge Cases

| Scenario | Expected Behavior |
|----------|-------------------|
| Financing denied | Display denial message with clear alternatives: try different financing or proceed with cash |
| No installation slots available | Allow order without scheduled date, indicate callback will be made to schedule |
| Homeowner wants to think about it | Enable "Send quote" without completing order; save session for continuation |
| Credit check timeout | Offer to retry or provide cash option as alternative |
| Multiple financing options available | Display all options with clear comparison of terms and monthly payments |
| Price changed since session started | Display notification of change, require acknowledgment before proceeding |

### Error States

| Error Condition | User Message | Recovery Action |
|-----------------|--------------|-----------------|
| Credit check denied | The financing application was not approved at this time. You can proceed with a cash payment or try a different financing option. | Show cash option prominently, offer alternative financing if available |
| Credit check system unavailable | We're having trouble connecting to the financing system. Please try again or proceed with a cash payment for now. | Retry action, cash fallback |
| Email send failed | We couldn't send the quote to that email address. Please verify and try again. | Highlight email field, allow retry |
| SMS send failed | We couldn't send the quote to that phone number. Please verify and try again. | Highlight phone field, allow retry |
| Scheduling system unavailable | Installation scheduling is temporarily unavailable. You can complete your order and we'll contact you to schedule. | Allow continuation without schedule |

