## 10. Deposit

### Goal

Collect the refundable deposit payment while reinforcing purchase confidence through social proof and clear refund terms.

### Journey

**Entry:**
- Summary & Checkout â†’ Deposit (after selections confirmed)

**Steps:**
1. System displays customer testimonials as social proof
2. System displays deposit amount with refund terms
3. Homeowner enters payment card information
4. Homeowner reviews terms and conditions acknowledgment
5. Homeowner submits deposit payment
6. System processes payment and confirms success

**Exit:**
- Payment successful â†’ Success
- Payment failed â†’ Display error with retry option
- Back â†’ Summary & Checkout

### Functionality

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Display social proof | Show 2-4 customer testimonials with ratings, quotes, names, and verification badges |
| Display deposit amount | Prominently show "$100 - Fully refundable" |
| Payment card entry | Secure form for card number, expiry, CVC, billing country, postal code |
| Display accepted payment methods | Show card brand logos (Visa, Mastercard, Amex, Discover) |
| Terms acknowledgment | Display terms link with acceptance language tied to submit action |
| Process payment | Submit payment to processor, handle success/failure |
| Payment confirmation | Display success state before redirecting to Success screen |

### Components

*Reference: engineering/design-system.md*

| Functionality | Recommended Components |
|---------------|------------------------|
| Testimonials display | Stacked/cascading card layout with star ratings, quote text, customer name/avatar, verification badge |
| Deposit amount | Emphasized heading with "Fully refundable" subtext |
| Payment form | PaymentForm component with card number, expiry, CVC fields |
| Card brand icons | Inline image display in card number field |
| Country selector | Dropdown/select input |
| Postal code | Input field |
| Terms text | Link text with acknowledgment copy |
| Submit action | Button (primary) with specific CTA: "Pay $100 refundable deposit" |
| Loading state | Button loading state during payment processing |
| Success confirmation | Checkmark animation before redirect |

### Edge Cases

| Scenario | Expected Behavior |
|----------|-------------------|
| Testimonials not available | Hide testimonials section, proceed with payment form only |
| International card | Accept valid international cards; adjust postal code validation by country |
| Card requires 3D Secure | Redirect to bank verification, handle return to complete flow |
| User navigates away during processing | Maintain payment state; check status on return |
| Deposit amount different from standard | Display actual amount (if promotional or adjusted) |

### Error States

| Error Condition | User Message | Recovery Action |
|-----------------|--------------|-----------------|
| Card declined | Your card was declined. Please check your card details or try a different card. | Clear sensitive fields, focus on card number |
| Invalid card number | Please enter a valid card number. | Highlight field, show validation hint |
| Expired card | This card has expired. Please use a different card. | Clear expiry field, focus for re-entry |
| Invalid CVC | Please enter a valid security code (3-4 digits on your card). | Highlight CVC field |
| Payment processing error | Something went wrong processing your payment. Your card has not been charged. Please try again. | Retry action |
| Network timeout | The payment is taking longer than expected. Please wait or try again. | Show loading state, offer retry after timeout |

