### Journey

**Entry:**
- Deposit â†’ Success (after payment confirmation)
- Direct link from confirmation email/text
- Homeowner dashboard navigation (if integrated)

**Steps:** (non-linear â€” homeowner reviews at any time)
- View order confirmation details
- See scheduled installation date
- Track project status (scheduled, in progress, complete)
- Access support contact if needed

**Exit:**
- Close/navigate away â†’ Session ends
- Contact support â†’ External support channel
- Change order notification â†’ Change Order screen

### Functionality

| Functionality | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| Display order confirmation | Confirmation number, equipment summary, total paid/owed |
| Show installation schedule | Confirmed date and time window for installation |
| Track project status | Visual timeline: Ordered â†’ Scheduled â†’ In Progress â†’ Complete |
| Display what to expect | Brief description of installation process and preparation steps |
